data.title: Delinquent property taxes in the Portland area
data.meta_description: People and businesses in Multnomah, Washington and Clackamas counties owed a combined $86 million in back taxes, and that doesn’t include the bills that came due Nov. 15. Below are individual properties with more than $10,000 in outstanding tax bills dating to 2012 or earlier. Note: The amounts for Clackamas County don’t include interest.
